I say it's time the Bat hang up his cape

29
00:03:24,204 --> 00:03:25,189
and call it a night.

30
00:03:25,213 --> 00:03:27,191
'Let a new hero actually get the job done.'

31
00:03:27,215 --> 00:03:28,205
It's not like it's your fault

32
00:03:28,229 --> 00:03:30,227
